# NOTE: index.xml is generated by the GitHub Action (.github/workflows/deploy.yml) and IS committed —
# it is the file users import into ReaPack, so it must NOT be ignored.
# NOTE: dev/, tests/, and docs/ stay tracked for development but are excluded from the installed
# package (they are not listed in Contour/contour.lua's @provides), so they never reach end users.
